scenes.description: Ayunda Risu talks to the audience in a cherry blossom park setting at night, encouraging the use of emojis and her 3D debut hashtag.
An announcement graphic for a Mini 3D Live Stream with Hololive Indonesia 1st Generation is shown.
Risu returns to the park setting, showing off her tail and giving a final message before the next segment.
A transition scene showing a pink bedroom where a small mascot version of Risu walks onto a chair.
An emotional voiceover section with glowing text appearing on screen against a dark background.
